---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-black shadow-lg">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: May 2, 2025</p>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            At Invisible Text, we value your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you use our website and services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We may collect various types of personal and non-personal information when you interact with our services, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Personal details like your name and email address</li>
            <li>Usage data including your IP address, browser type, and pages visited</li>
            <li>Information submitted through contact forms or feedback tools</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            The information we collect may be used for the following purposes:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>To operate and maintain our website</li>
            <li>To improve and personalize your experience</li>
            <li>To respond to your inquiries and provide support</li>
            <li>To analyze usage and trends to improve our services</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">4. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell your personal information. We may share your data with trusted third-party providers only when necessary to operate our services or comply with legal obligations.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain personal information only as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in this policy or as required by law. When no longer needed, data is securely deleted or anonymized.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">6. Security</h2>
          <p>
            We take appropriate measures to safeguard your personal information against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no internet transmission is ever 100% secure.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">7. Childrenâ€™s Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Our services are not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware of such data, we will take steps to delete it.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available on this page, with the effective date noted above.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">9. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at privacy@invisibletext.com.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
